{"word":"ὀχετεύω","slug":"ὀχετεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὀχετεύω</b></el> <el>(ὀχετεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὀχετός'><el>ὀχετός</el></a>\n<p/><i>to conduct</i> water <i>by a conduit</i> or <i>canal</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be conducted, conveyed</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ὠχετεύετο φάτις</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}